I have two calendar-related questions.

1.) There is a gadget for calendars but it only shows colored bars indicating that there is an item due on a specific date. Is there a gadget that would at least show the summary field?
2.) Is it possible to integrate the JIRA project calendar with an Outlook calendar (beyond just export it out as a iCal)? The idea would be that the JIRA data would synchronize with the user's Outlook (but only be read-only, of course, in Outlook).

