An example of what I'm hoping will be addressed in the next JIRA update. We have moved this ticket back and forth between MELSS and OpsEsc a couple times, each time it creates a new JIRA ticket number. I realize we can acccess it via any of the 4+ JIRA ticket numbers it has assigned for this one issue but it would eliminate much confusion if it would assume it's original JIRA ticket number in a project if it is moved back to a project where it has already been moved. Make sense? (it makes it difficult when we refer to the issue by a JIRA ticket number and the number is being incremented each time it is moved back and forth.) 

